title: Open Season - Original Soundtrack + Bonus Tracks
description:
This is the soundtrack to 2006&#039;s "Open Season" starring Martin Lawrence and Ashton Kutcher, featuring songs by Paul Westerberg. Tracks 1-12 are from the CD, plus I included a couple of audio clips I took from the film that most fans think should have been included on the soundtrack. Track 13 is "The Teddy Bear&#039;s Picnic" as sung by Debra Messing (Beth) and Track 14 is...wait for it..."The Magical Elf Song" as sung by Ashton Kutcher (Elliot). ;) Album cover art is also included. Contact me if you need this reseeded at sparky(at)theneitherworld.com
